data.description: Seller is offering to help with closing costs or interest rate buydown! Welcome to your beautifully maintained 4-bedroom, 3 bath home in the desirable and established community of South Fork. This home offers over 2,300 feet of living space with a thoughtfully laid out split floorplan, tile and vinyl flooring throughout, as well as a three-car garage. You will absolutely love this amazing kitchen which offers stainless steel appliances, a large island for family to gather around, granite counter tops with plenty of cabinet and counter space as well as a pantry and a breakfast nook. The owner’s suite features patio access, two walk in closets, a large walk-in shower and dual sinks. You will see the pride of ownership from the moment you step in. The large family room has separate sliders leading outside to the screened in patio. This home is absolutely move in ready and just waiting for you to call it home! South Fork is an amazing community and offers a community pool, park, basketball courts, playground, dog park & more! It is conveniently located to I-75 and 301 for easy commutes and access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and everything that the Tampa Bay area has to offer.
